Package dataAccess

Class AuthTokenAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • dataAccess.Accessor<AuthToken>
      • dataAccess.AuthTokenAccessor
  • public class AuthTokenAccessor
extends Accessor<AuthToken>
    A collection of methods that give access to AuthToken models in the database. It can create, delete, update, and find AuthTokens using a variety of methods.
